episode content to enhance promotional reach (09:10)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate with Gab on paid media campaign setup, target list, and creative asset review (16:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Participate in training call to understand paid campaign setup and retargeting code implementation (18:44)","completed":false},{"text":"Continue to develop matched audience list for LinkedIn targeting under Gab’s guidance (24:39)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
