WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    '6a9f190a-9e44-4b24-8f1d-d82022950bb9',
    '2025-11-20 13:30:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01K9YV0EP838A53BWYX7M8QPND',
    'Agrippon // New North Weekly Connect',
    '{"Shane Billings","Nathalie Mintjens","Nathalie Mintjens"}'::text[],
    1742,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83663022990?pwd=R1aTMdTGv2yblYfzlB6Wv1Sup4Z47U.1',
    '{"id":"01K9YV0EP838A53BWYX7M8QPND","title":"Agrippon // New North Weekly Connect","summary":{"notes":"## **Sales and Lead Management**\n\nThe team decided to immediately halt LinkedIn outreach by the current salesperson due to low engagement and no sign-ups, while exploring new sales staffing options. (00:00)\n\n- **Shane Billings** confirmed stopping all LinkedIn communication from the current salesperson, who had zero sign-ups despite networking efforts.\n- A new salesperson candidate is in early talks, with no commitment yet, aiming to revive LinkedIn outreach where most leads historically come from.\n- Shane highlighted a meeting scheduled with **Sandy Baird**, who expressed interest in the podcast but unclear about product involvement, using this as a relationship-building channel.\n- They plan to revert the website contact method from a direct Calendly link to a two-step process with a form first, to capture lead information more reliably after noticing many visitors drop off without filling anything out.\n\n## **Marketing Campaigns and Digital Presence**\n\nRecent updates to campaigns target new DSO and billing organization lists with refreshed ads and personalized landing pages, while social media presence is set for a strategic refresh. (00:03)\n\n- The **campaign refresh** launched new ad creatives and email sequences for DSOs and billing groups, including two new personalized landing pages sent to Shane for review.\n- The middle-funnel **nurturing campaign** targets warm website visitors by enriching account lists with relevant contacts to offer a free trial, supported by a tailored landing page.\n- Nathalie proposed using podcast clips and quote cards to increase LinkedIn posting frequency, which Shane approved for better audience engagement.\n- They agreed to rename the LinkedIn company page from **Pro Practice Solutions** to **Grip On** to align branding with ads and increase recognition.\n\n## **Website and User Experience Optimization**\n\nData shows higher average session time but fewer visitors, and a high drop-off on the contact page, prompting immediate form redesign and future sign-up page development. (00:10)\n\n- Website session length increased slightly, possibly due to new designs, but visitor numbers dropped as older campaigns slowed; the refreshed campaigns should boost traffic again.\n- LinkedIn ad cost per click dropped from **$13 to $12** after launching refreshed ads, with expectations for further improvement.\n- Shane and Nathalie agreed to revert the **contact page** from a direct salesperson Calendly link back to a Zoho form to better capture lead data and allow follow-up.\n- Shane plans to develop a self-service sign-up page to reduce sales friction, allowing direct purchases while still requiring sales contact for bulk discounts.\n\n## **Pricing Strategy and Revenue Model**\n\nThey are refining the pricing model to balance profitability with market acceptance, while exploring distributor and consultant partnerships with differentiated pricing and commission structures. (00:16)\n\n- Current pricing averages **$170 per office**, with discounts down to **$50 per office** for large batches; the model includes tiered batch pricing (e.g., five offices at **$745**, or **$150 per office**).\n- Early clients like **E Assist** paid $10 per office initially, which was not sustainable for growth; the team recognizes the need to increase prices.\n- Shane noted no direct feedback indicating prices are too high; instead, prospects often disengage quietly after price discussions.\n- Negotiations with a distributor propose a lower rate at **$129 per office** or **$90 per office** for five licenses, with the distributor responsible for onboarding, training, and first-level support, allowing them to mark up prices.\n- Consultant partnerships have not been engaged yet but are expected to operate on a flat commission fee, with the distributor model serving as a reference point.\n\n## **Operational and Process Improvements**\n\nThe team is prioritizing lead capture improvements, social media integration, and clearer communication flows to increase conversion and support scalability. (00:11)\n\n- Nathalie will immediately revert the contact page to a form-based lead capture system post-call to improve data collection and follow-up efficiency.\n- They plan to test different contact page copy and designs to reduce visitor drop-off and clarify expectations.\n- Integration of LinkedIn and Facebook posts via scheduling tools will streamline social media management and amplify brand presence with minimal extra effort.\n- Shane emphasized the need for clear roles in sales and support, with distributors expected to handle training and first-level support, reducing internal resource strain.\n\n## **Timelines and Next Steps**\n\nImmediate focus is on fixing lead capture forms, social media planning, and pricing research, with ongoing sales talks and a tentative meeting schedule around Thanksgiving. (00:26)\n\n- Nathalie will complete the form reversion, social media access verification, landing page delivery, and pricing research promptly after the call.\n- Shane requested Nathalie send a summary email with talking points by Wednesday for potential next-week discussions around Thanksgiving.\n- Sales hiring remains uncertain, with Shane and Dave monitoring progress and hopeful about the new salesperson or distributor deals.\n- No meetings planned for Thanksgiving; communication will continue via email and brief calls as needed.","outline":null,"keywords":["LinkedIn outreach","Sales campaign","Pricing strategy","Social media presence","Lead capture form","SaaS licensing"],"overview":"- **Sales Outreach Halted:** LinkedIn outreach paused due to low engagement; exploring new sales staffing options to revive efforts.  \n- **Updated Campaigns:** New ads and personalized landing pages launched for DSOs and billing organizations; nurturing campaign to offer free trials.  \n- **Website Optimization Needed:** Increased session time noted, but redesign contact page to capture leads; plan self-service sign-up to ease purchases.  \n- **Pricing Model Adjustments:** Current pricing averages $170 per office; exploring distributor partnerships for differentiated pricing and commission structures.  \n- **Process Improvements Prioritized:** Focus on enhancing lead capture, integrating social media, and clarifying roles to boost conversions and scalability.  \n- **Next Steps Outlined:** Immediate actions include form reversion, social media planning, and pricing research; follow-up discussions scheduled around Thanksgiving.","action_items":"\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nRevert “Contact Us” page from Calendly link back to Zoho form to capture lead data and integrate with scheduling (12:39)\nDevelop and send social media posting plan for LinkedIn and Facebook, including use of podcast clips and quote cards (07:19)\nVerify Facebook page access and confirm ability to post cross-platform with LinkedIn (09:19)\nSend personalized landing pages for review and feedback (03:09)\nConduct competitive research on pricing for SaaS platforms in space to inform pricing strategy (18:55)\nPrepare deck summarizing discussed material and send email with talking points midweek ahead of potential follow-up call (27:24)\n\n**Shane Billings**\nProvide Nathalie pricing details and feedback on past client pricing (E Assist pricing) to aid research (18:01)\nProvide access details or grant access as needed for social media management (Facebook, LinkedIn) (07:23)\nFollow up with potential new salesperson and keep Nathalie and Dave in the loop (28:27)\n\n**Unassigned**\nSchedule next meeting or communication after Thanksgiving week based on email update and Shane’s availability (27:24)\n"},"duration":29.030000686645508,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Shane Billings"},{"id":1,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"id":2,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Stop the.","index":0,"end_time":0.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That LinkedIn communication with her.","index":1,"end_time":2.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Right, yeah.","index":2,"end_time":4.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2.8,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Good.","index":3,"end_time":5.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":4.64,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":4,"end_time":6.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":5.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So nothing else is going out from her LinkedIn now.","index":5,"end_time":9.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":6.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":6,"end_time":10.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":9.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m in talks with another salesperson.","index":7,"end_time":14.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":11.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t know if we''ll bring them on or not.","index":8,"end_time":16.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":14.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Just.","index":9,"end_time":16.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":16.16,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We''re just starting the conversation, just looking, see what we can get.","index":10,"end_time":21.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":16.52,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":11,"end_time":23.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":22.64,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So, yeah, it was definitely good to have like someone on the LinkedIn side because that''s where we see the most responses.","index":12,"end_time":33.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":25.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I agree.","index":13,"end_time":35.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":34.69,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s unfortunate.","index":14,"end_time":37.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":36.37,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":15,"end_time":38.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":37.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But okay, yeah, we can start that up again if you find another salesperson.","index":16,"end_time":44.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":40.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then I know we had a couple of those conversations with Monique on LinkedIn, so we''ll just see the follow up with those.","index":17,"end_time":53.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":45.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Has she responded to any of those?","index":18,"end_time":54.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":53.11,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Haven''t looked.","index":19,"end_time":58.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":57.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Let me look real quick.","index":20,"end_time":59.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":58.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":21,"end_time":61.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":60.71,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Has she tried to sign up to anybody or is she just.","index":22,"end_time":64.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Sounds great.","index":23,"end_time":71.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.63,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":24,"end_time":72.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":71.99,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Nope.","index":25,"end_time":76.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":75.67,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Nope.","index":26,"end_time":77.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":76.63,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And no.","index":27,"end_time":78.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":77.43,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":28,"end_time":82.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":81.84,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Nothing.","index":29,"end_time":82.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":82.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, no.","index":30,"end_time":83.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":82.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Well, she kind of couched it in terms of networking, so, I mean, she can decide to network with them in general or not, so.","index":31,"end_time":98.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":87.52,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":32,"end_time":99.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":99.44,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":33,"end_time":103.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":102.8,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, good.","index":34,"end_time":107.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":107.37,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then the Sandy Baird one, the one from email.","index":35,"end_time":113.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":109.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I meet with her tomorrow.","index":36,"end_time":116.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":114.01,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Oh, she responded.","index":37,"end_time":118.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":116.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, we.","index":38,"end_time":119.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":118.73,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We set up a time to meet tomorrow.","index":39,"end_time":122.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":119.41,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean, we''ll see what that turns into.","index":40,"end_time":124.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":122.97,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s just a.","index":41,"end_time":126.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":125.05,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"She wants to be on the podcast.","index":42,"end_time":128.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":126.89,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t know, you know, if she''s interested in.","index":43,"end_time":134.059,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":128.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"In being involved with a grip on or not yet.","index":44,"end_time":137.539,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":134.059,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''s.","index":45,"end_time":140.899,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":138.819,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":46,"end_time":142.059,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":141.699,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The whole thought there was that the podcast is a way to just build that relationship.","index":47,"end_time":146.659,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":142.059,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":48,"end_time":147.619,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":147.139,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then also give you a way to organically bring up a grip on, see if it''s something that they want to write their clients.","index":49,"end_time":155.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":148.419,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":50,"end_time":159.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":156.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":51,"end_time":160.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":159.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then, so I know we have a lot of projects just like we''re working on right now, so I thought we could use today to just give you an update on where we are with them.","index":52,"end_time":171.339,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.46,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So for the campaign refresh.","index":53,"end_time":174.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":172.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So that''s for DSOs and billing orgs.","index":54,"end_time":176.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":174.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The new ad creatives that you reviewed and the email sequence have gone live.","index":55,"end_time":182.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":177.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So those are all good.","index":56,"end_time":184.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":183.03,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"This is targeting a whole new list of DSOs.","index":57,"end_time":187.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":185.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":58,"end_time":188.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":187.67,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then we also created the two personalized landing pages.","index":59,"end_time":193.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":189.91,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I''m going to send over to you so you can take a deeper look at the copy stuff.","index":60,"end_time":200.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":193.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, I mean, when you guys send me stuff, I just publish it.","index":61,"end_time":204.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":201.03,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m like, cool, okay.","index":62,"end_time":206.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":204.71,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You don''t want to look at it to see if it''s accurate?","index":63,"end_time":209.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":206.75,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Like some of the.","index":64,"end_time":210.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":209.76,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Right.","index":65,"end_time":210.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":210.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":66,"end_time":211.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":210.88,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You''ll send me that to review, right?","index":67,"end_time":212.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.2,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":68,"end_time":214.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":213.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll look at it.","index":69,"end_time":215.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":70,"end_time":216.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":215.76,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Is that.","index":71,"end_time":218.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":218,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay?","index":72,"end_time":219.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":219.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So those are all the pages.","index":73,"end_time":221.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":220.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s not just the new page that you just showed?","index":74,"end_time":223.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":221.68,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, this one.","index":75,"end_time":225.199,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":224.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That''s the landing page.","index":76,"end_time":226.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":225.2,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":77,"end_time":226.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":226.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The new Billers page.","index":78,"end_time":228.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":227.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yep.","index":79,"end_time":229.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":229.04,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Cool.","index":80,"end_time":230.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":229.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''m liking the web page.","index":81,"end_time":232.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":230.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I think it looks great.","index":82,"end_time":232.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":232.04,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it looks good too.","index":83,"end_time":235.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":233.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":84,"end_time":239.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":238.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then for that nurturing campaigns, this is the middle of the funnel part.","index":85,"end_time":243.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":239.93,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So you reviewed the email sequence this week.","index":86,"end_time":246.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":244.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":87,"end_time":248.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":247.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I made the updates that you had left.","index":88,"end_time":250.729,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":248.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then we''re working on right now is crafting the actual contact list.","index":89,"end_time":255.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":251.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So taking all of the website visits that we''ve had in the past that we sent over to you, if you remember, those are mostly just.","index":90,"end_time":264,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":255.61,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We only have the account name.","index":91,"end_time":266.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":264,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We don''t have any specific contact details.","index":92,"end_time":268.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":266.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we''re taking those accounts and then finding people with relevant job titles in those companies to use as our list to start sending these out.","index":93,"end_time":277.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":269,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, and then this is the email campaign you''re talking about?","index":94,"end_time":283.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":278.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, this is the email campaign.","index":95,"end_time":285,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":283.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And if you remember, for these people, since they''re kind of warm already, we wanted to give them the free trial offer.","index":96,"end_time":292.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":285.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, that sounds fine.","index":97,"end_time":294.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":292.96,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We also have a landing page that specifically talks about that.","index":98,"end_time":297.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":294.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So this over to you as well.","index":99,"end_time":300.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":298.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":100,"end_time":301.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":301.2,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Cool.","index":101,"end_time":304.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":303.92,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then once.","index":102,"end_time":306,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":304.32,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":103,"end_time":307.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":306.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then after that, then we''ll also be making image ads for this offer for LinkedIn, so promoting the free trial as well.","index":104,"end_time":314,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":307.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":105,"end_time":316.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":314.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then those were all of my priorities.","index":106,"end_time":318.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":316.84,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then what I''ll be working on next is that E assist sequence for the indirect clients.","index":107,"end_time":324.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":318.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":108,"end_time":328.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":325.38,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Before going into the data, any.","index":109,"end_time":332.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":329.22,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Any other notes on the projects that we''re working on?","index":110,"end_time":335.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":332.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No, let''s keep going.","index":111,"end_time":337.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":335.86,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I. I heard.","index":112,"end_time":338.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":337.22,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Well, I did some.","index":113,"end_time":339.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":338.42,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"One of the things I thought was interesting is I went and just.","index":114,"end_time":343.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":339.7,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I thought we had a Facebook page.","index":115,"end_time":345.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":344.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":116,"end_time":346.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":345.82,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean, we do, but I think it''s empty and our LinkedIn page has been dry for a while.","index":117,"end_time":355.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":346.14,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What do you think?","index":118,"end_time":356.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":355.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"How important is it to create more of a.","index":119,"end_time":359.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":356.63,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We.","index":120,"end_time":359.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":359.67,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We got away from Facebook ads.","index":121,"end_time":361.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":359.99,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t have any.","index":122,"end_time":363.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":362.79,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t have.","index":123,"end_time":367.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":366.39,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Oh, gosh, Instagram.","index":124,"end_time":372.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":370.47,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t have Instagram.","index":125,"end_time":373.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":372.39,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We have YouTube.","index":126,"end_time":376.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":375.92,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We put stuff out on there.","index":127,"end_time":378,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":376.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"How important do you think it is to have more of a presence and a page for LinkedIn and Facebook?","index":128,"end_time":385.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":379.52,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I know we got away from the ads in Facebook, but what are your thoughts?","index":129,"end_time":389.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":385.84,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"LinkedIn, I definitely say, is more important, especially because we have the ads running and we''re doing outbound there.","index":130,"end_time":397.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":390.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"There''s a chance that people do click on, like, the company name.","index":131,"end_time":400.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":397.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And once they click on it, they do want to see that it''s a legit company and that by the fact that you''re posting consistently.","index":132,"end_time":407.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":401.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, so we do.","index":133,"end_time":410.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":408.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s legit.","index":134,"end_time":411.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":410.84,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It looks good.","index":135,"end_time":412.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":411.64,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t post frequently.","index":136,"end_time":413.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":412.2,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Is that something that you guys could take on and help us post frequently?","index":137,"end_time":417.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":414.04,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Is that something we could do?","index":138,"end_time":419,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":417.92,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, definitely.","index":139,"end_time":420.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":419.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And what we also do is, like, because when we create the podcast episodes, we create those clips and quote cards and stuff, so we can use that to create posts.","index":140,"end_time":431.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":421.32,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe even if that would be great.","index":141,"end_time":433.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":431.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, if that''s something that we could ask you to do, I think that would be good.","index":142,"end_time":439.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":435.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":143,"end_time":440.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":439.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Let me make a note.","index":144,"end_time":443.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":442.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And if you need access to that, you just shoot me who you need access.","index":145,"end_time":447.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":443.98,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I think I add people or you may already have access.","index":146,"end_time":450.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":447.82,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m not quite sure.","index":147,"end_time":451.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":450.86,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, I think we already do because we manage the paid campaigns.","index":148,"end_time":457.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":149,"end_time":458.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":457.79,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What would your thoughts be on changing the LinkedIn name to a Grip on instead of Pro Practice Solutions?","index":150,"end_time":465.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":458.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, I''m okay with it.","index":151,"end_time":468.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":467.55,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean, a grip on, like, obviously, you know how our company is structured.","index":152,"end_time":473.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":469.39,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, open to it.","index":153,"end_time":476.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":474.43,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s fine.","index":154,"end_time":477.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":476.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":155,"end_time":478.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":477.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that''ll help since, like, the ads, all of the logos on the ads are a grip on.","index":156,"end_time":486.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":481.55,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That makes sense.","index":157,"end_time":488.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":487.92,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It should still be a grip on.","index":158,"end_time":490.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":489.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":159,"end_time":491.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":491.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, Cool.","index":160,"end_time":493.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":491.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I''ll be back next time with a.","index":161,"end_time":496.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":494.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Just some ideas for what we can start doing on social.","index":162,"end_time":499.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":496.8,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":163,"end_time":500.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":500.16,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So.","index":164,"end_time":501.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":500.64,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But yeah, let''s.","index":165,"end_time":503.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":502.16,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Let''s get on that.","index":166,"end_time":504.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Let''s start to make ourselves.","index":167,"end_time":505.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":504.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then Facebook is literally blank.","index":168,"end_time":508.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":505.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":169,"end_time":509.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":508.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I don''t know if that matters at all, but.","index":170,"end_time":512.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":509.99,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Facebook is not one that we typically do a lot of just because it is more B2C.","index":171,"end_time":519.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":514.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":172,"end_time":520.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":520.23,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Well, yeah, I mean, I know that there''s a lot of dental organizations out on Facebook with a lot of groups.","index":173,"end_time":532.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":522.31,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So I think just having something there, not necessarily, you know, like a lot of effort, but probably should put something on the page to say, hey, we''re a Grip On.","index":174,"end_time":544.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":532.59,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, Go to link.","index":175,"end_time":547.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":545.71,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Go to LinkedIn is what it should say.","index":176,"end_time":549.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":547.43,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Right.","index":177,"end_time":550.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":549.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We can.","index":178,"end_time":551.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":550.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"When we, like, we use a tool to schedule posts on LinkedIn, we can actually that it schedules on both platforms at the same time.","index":179,"end_time":559.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":551.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":180,"end_time":560.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":559.71,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"More work.","index":181,"end_time":561.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":560.91,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, that would be good.","index":182,"end_time":563.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":562.11,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll look after this.","index":183,"end_time":565.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":563.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"If we have access to Facebook.","index":184,"end_time":566.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''m not sure.","index":185,"end_time":567.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":567,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, well, I know you have access to Facebook because we were.","index":186,"end_time":572.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":568.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I gave you keys to the kingdom, last I remember.","index":187,"end_time":574.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":572.04,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I just don''t.","index":188,"end_time":575.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":574.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t know what that means.","index":189,"end_time":576.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":575.32,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Or how extensive that is.","index":190,"end_time":578.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":576.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But yeah, I think, you know, we have like I saw on the emails you had the Facebook link and the, and the LinkedIn link and I think I put a note on there.","index":191,"end_time":589.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":578.76,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m like these up to date kind of thing.","index":192,"end_time":591.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":589.76,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Are we doing like, I think it wasn''t even Instagram.","index":193,"end_time":593.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":591.64,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m like, do we do Instagram?","index":194,"end_time":595.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":593.8,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So if.","index":195,"end_time":596.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":595.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m not saying we have to build it out amazingly, but we probably should have something, especially if we''re sending out links to those things.","index":196,"end_time":603.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":596.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":197,"end_time":604.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":604.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":198,"end_time":605.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":605.01,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":199,"end_time":607.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":607.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Dave, what are your thoughts on any of this?","index":200,"end_time":613.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":611.49,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":201,"end_time":616.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":615.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":202,"end_time":618.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":618.13,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":203,"end_time":621.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":621.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then looking at the data.","index":204,"end_time":625.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":623.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So for the website, the average session length has increased slightly maybe due to the designs.","index":205,"end_time":633.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":625.66,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe it''s more engaging, people have more places to navigate to.","index":206,"end_time":636.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":633.58,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"While the actual session lengths are lower.","index":207,"end_time":640.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":638.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The number of visitors coming is reducing, likely because those campaigns are slowing down the.","index":208,"end_time":647.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":641.34,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So with the refreshed campaign to DSOs and Billers, we should start to see that start to climb again.","index":209,"end_time":654.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":647.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":210,"end_time":655.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":654.58,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then for our LinkedIn ads, so our average cost per click has reduced to 12.","index":211,"end_time":661.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It was previously 13.","index":212,"end_time":662.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":661.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Those refreshed ads were launched yesterday.","index":213,"end_time":667.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":665.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we should see that continue to go down going forward.","index":214,"end_time":671.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":668.58,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That would be good because it''s pretty dang high.","index":215,"end_time":674.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":672.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":216,"end_time":675.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":675.31,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And what''s interesting about the data.","index":217,"end_time":678.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":676.75,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Are you going to pull up the data?","index":218,"end_time":679.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":678.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":219,"end_time":680.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":679.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":220,"end_time":681.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":680.91,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What''s interesting to me about the data is the number of people who go to contact us and don''t fill out anything.","index":221,"end_time":692.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":684.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t know if that''s normal.","index":222,"end_time":697.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":695.87,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It actually that brings up a good point of I think we will need to change this back to the form.","index":223,"end_time":709.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":700.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Right.","index":224,"end_time":710.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":710.58,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Because it''s her.","index":225,"end_time":711.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":711.14,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":226,"end_time":713.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":712.82,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Link.","index":227,"end_time":713.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":713.22,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And.","index":228,"end_time":718.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":717.86,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, the new guy that we''re talking to hopefully comes on board.","index":229,"end_time":725.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":722.58,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That would help.","index":230,"end_time":727.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":726.59,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You know, if she gets an invite.","index":231,"end_time":730.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":729.23,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m hoping she doesn''t.","index":232,"end_time":732.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":730.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Do we get any indication that she got an invite?","index":233,"end_time":735.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":732.67,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"No, we have no idea what happens.","index":234,"end_time":740.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":736.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t even know if people have been asking to come and she''s not paying attention.","index":235,"end_time":745.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":740.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":236,"end_time":746.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":746.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"This is linked directly to her email.","index":237,"end_time":750.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":747.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":238,"end_time":754.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":754.12,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We need to.","index":239,"end_time":754.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":754.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We need to change this back to a form.","index":240,"end_time":756.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":754.76,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":241,"end_time":757.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":757.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We''Ll see if the new guy wants it to be a director''s calendly.","index":242,"end_time":764.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":759.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But my feeling is, is this is.","index":243,"end_time":768.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":765,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean this isn''t good.","index":244,"end_time":772.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":771,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So.","index":245,"end_time":773.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":773,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean there is benefit to having even with the new salesperson just having the form here as the first step one because it allows you to collect the information.","index":246,"end_time":789.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":776.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Like right now if someone were to book you don''t.","index":247,"end_time":792.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":790.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Is There a way to have Calendly send a form in and an invite.","index":248,"end_time":799.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":792.93,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Is that a.","index":249,"end_time":800.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":799.49,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So we can.","index":250,"end_time":802.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":801.25,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We could add a form, which is the first step.","index":251,"end_time":805.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":802.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Once they submit it, then they''re shown the Calendly link.","index":252,"end_time":808.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":806.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":253,"end_time":810.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":810.06,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean, that''s two steps.","index":254,"end_time":812.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":810.7,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I wonder if they''re gonna follow through.","index":255,"end_time":813.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":812.14,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But I guess if they do the first form, we could reach out and say, hey, we saw you fill out the form.","index":256,"end_time":818.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":813.78,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":257,"end_time":819.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":818.38,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":258,"end_time":819.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":819.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":259,"end_time":820.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":820.3,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"This probably needs to be changed quickly considering that Monique is not here.","index":260,"end_time":824.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":820.78,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, we can get on that.","index":261,"end_time":830.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":825.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Can get that right after this call.","index":262,"end_time":832.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":831.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Very good.","index":263,"end_time":833.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":833.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":264,"end_time":834.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":834.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":265,"end_time":837.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":836.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":266,"end_time":841.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":840.86,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":267,"end_time":848.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":848.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then in terms of your question of the drop off from this page, it is pretty normal.","index":268,"end_time":852.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":848.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, people are exploring.","index":269,"end_time":854.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":852.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"They''re not always ready to immediately reach out to someone.","index":270,"end_time":857.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":854.38,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"What we can do though is try different copy, see if.","index":271,"end_time":861.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":857.58,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":272,"end_time":862.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":861.93,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You can redesign this and see what.","index":273,"end_time":864.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":862.41,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yep, I''m open to that.","index":274,"end_time":865.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":864.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":275,"end_time":866.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":866.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We can test some things out.","index":276,"end_time":869.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":868.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Why this is not loading.","index":277,"end_time":876.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":875.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"There we go.","index":278,"end_time":882.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":881.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":279,"end_time":883.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":882.73,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean, if you look at that contact of 63 people.","index":280,"end_time":886.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":883.09,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":281,"end_time":889.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":888.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And we''re getting none of them.","index":282,"end_time":890.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":889.42,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And that''s.","index":283,"end_time":894.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":893.66,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s.","index":284,"end_time":895.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":894.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That seems like a lot.","index":285,"end_time":896.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":895.14,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":286,"end_time":897.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":897.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean.","index":287,"end_time":901.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":900.86,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":288,"end_time":902.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":901.98,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"More and more people are starting to do self education before ever reaching out.","index":289,"end_time":907.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":902.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I wonder.","index":290,"end_time":910.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":909.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I could see that on the rest of the system, but not on the Contact Us page.","index":291,"end_time":916.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":911.9,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You know what you''re going to get on a Contact Us page.","index":292,"end_time":918.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":916.14,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":293,"end_time":919.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":919.37,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Or maybe they.","index":294,"end_time":922.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":921.21,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe they think it''s like a.","index":295,"end_time":923.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":922.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"You know, for some tools.","index":296,"end_time":925.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":924.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"When you say get it now, you''re able to just sign up on this.","index":297,"end_time":929.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":925.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m actually.","index":298,"end_time":930.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":929.05,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s one of the things that I want to develop next is that they can just sign up and not have to worry about us taking a call.","index":299,"end_time":939.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":930.97,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":300,"end_time":940.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":939.77,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''m just letting you know because at some point we''ll have to add a page that lets them sign up the.","index":301,"end_time":950.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":944.09,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And we may have to design that page and then have it tie into our system.","index":302,"end_time":955.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":951.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The thing that is interesting from that point of view is they''ll still need to contact sales if they want a bulk discount because we''re not gonna.","index":303,"end_time":966.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":956.12,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We''re just gonna do my office.","index":304,"end_time":967.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.24,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":305,"end_time":969,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":968.44,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Anyway, I think that''d be.","index":306,"end_time":971.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":969.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think that would actually work really well because it sounds like.","index":307,"end_time":974,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":971.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, get a grip on.","index":308,"end_time":974.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":974,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"They''re like, oh, I can sign up right now.","index":309,"end_time":976.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":974.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"See what it actually looks like people are wanting to speak to salespeople less and less.","index":310,"end_time":981.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":976.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, I see.","index":311,"end_time":983.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":982.38,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I see.","index":312,"end_time":983.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":983.34,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So get a grip on is you think they''re actually thinking that they''re ordering it.","index":313,"end_time":987.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":983.86,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":314,"end_time":988.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":988.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Might be.","index":315,"end_time":989.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":988.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I wonder.","index":316,"end_time":990.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":990.14,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"See, this is one of the things that I''ve been debating, and this is something that Dave and Natalie, I could use your help on.","index":317,"end_time":1003.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":992.14,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t know the.","index":318,"end_time":1004.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1003.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The price point to get this thing.","index":319,"end_time":1006.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1004.63,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And when we.","index":320,"end_time":1007.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1006.95,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The reason we haven''t published a price point on the website is because we don''t know it.","index":321,"end_time":1013.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1007.75,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We''ll go into meetings with people and they''ll be like, yeah, this is.","index":322,"end_time":1016.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1013.51,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"This is a good price or it''s a bad price.","index":323,"end_time":1020.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1018.31,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t know.","index":324,"end_time":1021.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1020.629,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And we want to maximize our revenue by getting the right price point as high as we can get it, obviously.","index":325,"end_time":1027.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1021.99,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But once you publish it, you''re locked in.","index":326,"end_time":1029.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1027.31,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Right.","index":327,"end_time":1030.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1029.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You can''t change it after that.","index":328,"end_time":1031.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1030.15,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s why we haven''t done it.","index":329,"end_time":1032.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1031.79,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t know how to navigate those waters if we don''t have a lot of people to sign up and hear their feedback.","index":330,"end_time":1043.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1036.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Regarding price point.","index":331,"end_time":1044.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1043.43,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":332,"end_time":1046.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1046.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s not uncommon to not have price on the website for.","index":333,"end_time":1051.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1047.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":334,"end_time":1052.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1051.87,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, Actually, I''d say it''s more often than not, you see that there''s no price on the website.","index":335,"end_time":1058.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1052.83,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s only once you''re actually in the sales process, then you learn what the price is.","index":336,"end_time":1062.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1058.91,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I gotcha.","index":337,"end_time":1064.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1063.49,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":338,"end_time":1066.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1065.97,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s good to know.","index":339,"end_time":1067.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1066.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If we do go where you can just sign up and order it, we''ll have to pick one price point.","index":340,"end_time":1072.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1067.57,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":341,"end_time":1073.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1073.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Natalie, I don''t know if you have ways to figure that out.","index":342,"end_time":1079.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1075.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, let me think on it.","index":343,"end_time":1083.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe if you''re able to share like E Assist, for example, or ones that you have sold, what the price point was.","index":344,"end_time":1089.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1083.89,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So E Assist is.","index":345,"end_time":1091.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1089.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Was our first client.","index":346,"end_time":1093.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1092.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"They were at $10 an office.","index":347,"end_time":1096.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1094.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Huh.","index":348,"end_time":1098.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1097.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That is nowhere near where we need to be in order to be profitable.","index":349,"end_time":1103,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1098.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":350,"end_time":1104.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1104.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And now they''re unlimited licenses for 15 grand a month.","index":351,"end_time":1109.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1105.56,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":352,"end_time":1111.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1111.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And that averages out to be a little bit more than $10 an office.","index":353,"end_time":1118.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1114.04,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But that''s crazy.","index":354,"end_time":1122.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1120.82,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"No, I mean, that''s not going to work.","index":355,"end_time":1125.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1122.9,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, it got us off the ground.","index":356,"end_time":1128.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1126.02,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We can''t grow with that revenue.","index":357,"end_time":1130.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1128.1,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yep.","index":358,"end_time":1132.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1131.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":359,"end_time":1134.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1134.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So.","index":360,"end_time":1135.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1135.22,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":361,"end_time":1139.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1138.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then I can also look at other SaaS platforms in this space, even if they''re not competitors.","index":362,"end_time":1145.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1139.14,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But just what''s the general price point that they''re charging?","index":363,"end_time":1147.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1145.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":364,"end_time":1149.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1148.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You''re going to find that that''s going to be in the hundreds of dollars.","index":365,"end_time":1152.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1149.37,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":366,"end_time":1154.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1153.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And even though they''re not competitors, we are competing in the budget category.","index":367,"end_time":1161.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1157.29,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Right.","index":368,"end_time":1161.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1161.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Meaning they''ve got a software budget, so we''ve got to fit in.","index":369,"end_time":1165.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1161.93,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And I can send you.","index":370,"end_time":1167.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1166.41,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''ll just cut and paste what our pricing model currently is or what we think it should be.","index":371,"end_time":1178.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1168.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Let me just send that to you.","index":372,"end_time":1180.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1178.9,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":373,"end_time":1182.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1181.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right.","index":374,"end_time":1190.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1190.14,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And we do it, we, we do it in bull.","index":375,"end_time":1195.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1192.94,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"In batches.","index":376,"end_time":1197.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1195.98,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So you buy batches of licenses, 5, 10, 20 or so and so forth.","index":377,"end_time":1201.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1197.1,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So you buy the whole batch anyway.","index":378,"end_time":1206.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1201.94,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Does that mean like you''re buying for five offices?","index":379,"end_time":1213.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1211,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, you buy, you can buy one office or five offices or 10 offices and so forth.","index":380,"end_time":1219.639,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1214.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":381,"end_time":1220.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1219.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And so the way that would work is you would.","index":382,"end_time":1226.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1222.36,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I just send it to you.","index":383,"end_time":1228.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1227.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You would purchase.","index":384,"end_time":1229.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1228.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And our price model is 170 an office.","index":385,"end_time":1232.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1230.17,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":386,"end_time":1234.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1233.85,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But if you buy five offices, you get all five licenses, fill them however you want for $745.","index":387,"end_time":1241.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1234.65,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That ends up being $150 an office.","index":388,"end_time":1246.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1243.21,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So you save a ton and as you go up, it can get as low as 120 an office.","index":389,"end_time":1251.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1246.49,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Or if you buy, you know, 500 offices, it''s like $50 an office.","index":390,"end_time":1255.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1251.29,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":391,"end_time":1256.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1256.25,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So now is that too high?","index":392,"end_time":1260.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1257.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":393,"end_time":1260.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1260.17,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We had other thoughts where we started out at 99 an office just to stay sub 100.","index":394,"end_time":1265.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1260.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":395,"end_time":1267.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1266.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Have you ever gotten feedback that it''s too high?","index":396,"end_time":1270.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1268.57,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No.","index":397,"end_time":1271.889,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1271.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What we get is, is that we go into talk price and then people wander off until we''re like, okay, was that too high?","index":398,"end_time":1278.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1271.889,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And you''re just not telling us?","index":399,"end_time":1279.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1278.37,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":400,"end_time":1281.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1280.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Like the last person that we got, Monique, was working with them to close them.","index":401,"end_time":1284.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1281.21,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"They just stopped talking to us.","index":402,"end_time":1291.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1286.37,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"This is interesting.","index":403,"end_time":1293.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1292.29,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So they stopped talking to us.","index":404,"end_time":1294.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1293.29,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"She couldn''t get in response to them.","index":405,"end_time":1297.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1294.97,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And I don''t know what she did to try.","index":406,"end_time":1299.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1298.13,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I just know she said she tried.","index":407,"end_time":1301.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1299.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then later I saw that she actually looked at our BAA agreement through.","index":408,"end_time":1307.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1302.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You know, when you sign online, that website just basically told me, hey, they looked at your agreement.","index":409,"end_time":1318,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1312.64,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And a BAA is not the contract.","index":410,"end_time":1323.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1321.36,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It just says, hey, you''re going to be involved in a hipaa.","index":411,"end_time":1326.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1323.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"HIPAA relationship with us.","index":412,"end_time":1328.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1326.56,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Here''s how both of us should be.","index":413,"end_time":1329.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1328.12,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And the government requires that document, so it doesn''t carry any obligation.","index":414,"end_time":1336.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1329.68,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But they looked at it.","index":415,"end_time":1339.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1338.48,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So I''m like, okay, are you guys not doing it now?","index":416,"end_time":1342.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1339.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But when, when they first looked at it, they were super interested.","index":417,"end_time":1345.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1342.16,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But anyway, here we are.","index":418,"end_time":1346.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1345.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":419,"end_time":1347.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1347.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Did they ever try get the free trial?","index":420,"end_time":1350.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1348.32,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No.","index":421,"end_time":1352.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1352,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And we offered it to them.","index":422,"end_time":1353.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1352.36,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We were like, pick your hardest office.","index":423,"end_time":1356.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1354.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Even with the free trial.","index":424,"end_time":1357.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1356.64,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s why we''re like, free trials.","index":425,"end_time":1359.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1357.76,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Still have to sign the baa.","index":426,"end_time":1360.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1359.16,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You know, We didn''t even get that far.","index":427,"end_time":1371.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1363.29,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":428,"end_time":1372.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1371.77,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":429,"end_time":1374.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1374.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I wonder what, what it was.","index":430,"end_time":1376.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1374.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So they had Seen the price by that point, right?","index":431,"end_time":1379.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1376.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, this is.","index":432,"end_time":1382.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1381.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And the price that I sent you is the one that they saw.","index":433,"end_time":1384.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1382.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And the feedback we got was, oh, that''s in our budget.","index":434,"end_time":1388.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1385.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So they didn''t balk at all.","index":435,"end_time":1391.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1390.3,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then they.","index":436,"end_time":1393.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1393.02,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But then they didn''t.","index":437,"end_time":1394.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1393.74,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"They stopped responding.","index":438,"end_time":1395.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1394.62,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So I don''t know.","index":439,"end_time":1397.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1395.98,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And it would be great to at least hear, like, why didn''t you.","index":440,"end_time":1401.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1398.38,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":441,"end_time":1404.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1403.66,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Are.","index":442,"end_time":1405.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1404.619,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Do you have any contact with the person or was it only.","index":443,"end_time":1408.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1405.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":444,"end_time":1409.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1408.86,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But if I get a new salesperson, I''ll stick them on them.","index":445,"end_time":1412.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1409.46,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":446,"end_time":1413.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1412.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I.","index":447,"end_time":1414.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1413.66,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You don''t want me selling.","index":448,"end_time":1416.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1415.12,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Why not?","index":449,"end_time":1419.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1419.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Because I would probably lose more than now.","index":450,"end_time":1426.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1421.92,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I will say we are still talking to another group who wants to be a distributor for us.","index":451,"end_time":1435.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.2,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":452,"end_time":1437.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1437.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And we have quoted them a pricing model that''s lower so that they can be enticed.","index":453,"end_time":1444.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1438.24,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And for them it''s 129 an office, 450 for five, which is $90 per office for five licenses.","index":454,"end_time":1454.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1445.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then they can charge above that and pocket the difference.","index":455,"end_time":1459.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1455.69,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So we''re in talks with them to try to figure out what that looks like.","index":456,"end_time":1464.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1460.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And of course they got busy and now we''re going to follow up in early next week.","index":457,"end_time":1468.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1464.57,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But that we''re hopeful that.","index":458,"end_time":1473.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1472.22,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And they have a sales team and clients that they''re going to try to push this on.","index":459,"end_time":1477.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1473.46,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So we''re hopeful there.","index":460,"end_time":1478.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1477.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Nice.","index":461,"end_time":1479.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1479.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Would that be the same pricing model for consultants?","index":462,"end_time":1483.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1479.98,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We haven''t.","index":463,"end_time":1486.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1486.14,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I think we would go a commission model for consultants and we''re offering just a flat commission fee.","index":464,"end_time":1498.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1486.94,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":465,"end_time":1500.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1499.43,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And.","index":466,"end_time":1503.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1503.03,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But see, here''s the thing.","index":467,"end_time":1504.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1503.43,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean, maybe there''s a different model.","index":468,"end_time":1506.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1504.67,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"There.","index":469,"end_time":1506.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1506.63,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But we haven''t engaged any consultants yet to kind of explore that with them, if that makes sense.","index":470,"end_time":1515.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1509.91,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, I suppose so.","index":471,"end_time":1518.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1515.75,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"One of the reasons, by the way, so just so you''re aware, one of the reasons it''s lower is because we actually ask you to do things.","index":472,"end_time":1525.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1518.35,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Like I''m going to ask them to do things.","index":473,"end_time":1527.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1525.76,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Training, onboarding, first level IDT support and adoption.","index":474,"end_time":1532.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1527.68,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So it doesn''t come free.","index":475,"end_time":1535.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1533.92,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Like, it''s not just free.","index":476,"end_time":1536.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1535.68,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Like I''m actually expecting you to do those things.","index":477,"end_time":1539.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1536.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":478,"end_time":1540.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1539.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we don''t have to.","index":479,"end_time":1541.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1540.56,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s.","index":480,"end_time":1541.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1541.52,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s part of why.","index":481,"end_time":1542.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1541.96,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And first level support is like, oh, you forgot your password.","index":482,"end_time":1545.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1542.96,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Like, you know.","index":483,"end_time":1547.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1545.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":484,"end_time":1547.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1547.37,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So that''s that.","index":485,"end_time":1550.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1550.01,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s funny because if you forget your password, you can also just say, I forgot my password and it''s the same thing, but.","index":486,"end_time":1556.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1551.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So there''s not a whole lot of extra work.","index":487,"end_time":1559.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1558.17,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But I Am asking them to take phone calls regarding the support and so forth.","index":488,"end_time":1564.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1559.85,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, gotcha.","index":489,"end_time":1566.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1564.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":490,"end_time":1567.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1567.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll see how the conversation tomorrow goes with the consultant.","index":491,"end_time":1571.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1567.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":492,"end_time":1572.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1572.02,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If there''s anything there.","index":493,"end_time":1573.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1572.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":494,"end_time":1575.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1575.22,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yep.","index":495,"end_time":1577.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1576.5,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"All right, then.","index":496,"end_time":1580.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1579.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So from my side.","index":497,"end_time":1581.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1580.82,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we''ll.","index":498,"end_time":1582.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1581.94,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We''ll work on this form right after this.","index":499,"end_time":1584.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1582.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Get it changed back to a Zoho form so we can capture any information.","index":500,"end_time":1588.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1585.22,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll come up with a plan for social, both LinkedIn and Facebook.","index":501,"end_time":1594.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1590.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll check that we have access to Facebook, and then I''ll send over those landing pages that we talked about.","index":502,"end_time":1603.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1594.58,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then also do some more research on the price point as well.","index":503,"end_time":1607.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1603.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, that would be helpful.","index":504,"end_time":1610.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1608.35,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":505,"end_time":1610.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1610.27,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And no rush on the price point because we''re not locked in at any.","index":506,"end_time":1615.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1611.47,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You know what I''m saying?","index":507,"end_time":1616.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1615.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":508,"end_time":1616.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1616.27,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Like, it''s not like it''s got to go out right away because we''re not locked in.","index":509,"end_time":1619.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1616.63,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We''re locked in when I put it online and we''re charging a fee for the service.","index":510,"end_time":1626.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1620.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s when we''re locked in.","index":511,"end_time":1627.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1626.47,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So I have to develop that ability in the system.","index":512,"end_time":1631.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1627.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So just to give you an idea.","index":513,"end_time":1633.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1631.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":514,"end_time":1635.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1633.83,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right, great.","index":515,"end_time":1637.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1636.23,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then I know next week.","index":516,"end_time":1641.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1640.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Next Thursday is Thanksgiving.","index":517,"end_time":1643.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1642.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re fine.","index":518,"end_time":1645.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1644.31,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You don''t have to meet on Thanksgiving.","index":519,"end_time":1646.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1645.15,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":520,"end_time":1649.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1648.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But would you like to meet some other time during the week?","index":521,"end_time":1652.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1649.91,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Goodness.","index":522,"end_time":1654.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1654.51,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Let''s start with an email.","index":523,"end_time":1661.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1659.63,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Could you send me an email Wednesday, just with some talking points of.","index":524,"end_time":1666.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1661.95,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And hopefully we can skip it, but if not, then I might just give you a quick call and say, hey, I got some things.","index":525,"end_time":1674.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1669.47,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":526,"end_time":1676.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1675.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But, yeah, let''s.","index":527,"end_time":1678.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1677.71,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, just, you know, shoot me an email probably.","index":528,"end_time":1682.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1679.96,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''d be most interested in the things we just discussed.","index":529,"end_time":1685.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1682.96,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":530,"end_time":1688.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1687.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, Yeah, I can even.","index":531,"end_time":1691.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1689.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll put all the information into a deck, like what I usually do and send that over email, and we''ll see if there''s anything else you''d like to discuss.","index":532,"end_time":1699.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1691.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yep.","index":533,"end_time":1700.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1700.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Thank you, Dave.","index":534,"end_time":1702.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1700.8,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Have I forgotten anything?","index":535,"end_time":1703.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1702.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"No, sounds good.","index":536,"end_time":1705.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1704.2,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":537,"end_time":1707.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1706.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Copy Dave on that email, too.","index":538,"end_time":1709.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1707.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So he''s.","index":539,"end_time":1710.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1709.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And I''m gonna.","index":540,"end_time":1713.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1712.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Hopefully.","index":541,"end_time":1714.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1713.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean, we''re talking.",