reach-HubSpot automatic contact creation workflow is live to reduce manual data entry (35:12)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate internally on what extra steps are needed to optimize lead management and first meeting generation (32:52)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist Colin with setting up tasks related to the contact enrichment and HubSpot workflows as needed (09:04)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
