WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    '6061d0c2-de11-40b9-8824-1ccd80a970d6',
    '2025-11-19 16:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01K9WPQCCE3R9ZYQ4F1YKT0KP7',
    'GSS // MID Weekly Meeting',
    '{"Will Fleming","Baylee Gunnell","Nick S (GSS)","Will Fleming"}'::text[],
    1895,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83236942727?pwd=NaLGKm3JEGM6umJeSVS9pHPmDfNAYN.1',
    '{"id":"01K9WPQCCE3R9ZYQ4F1YKT0KP7","title":"GSS // MID Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Conference and Networking Impact**\n\nThe team gained valuable industry connections and confidence at the recent conference, setting the stage for future business opportunities. \n\n- **Nick S (GSS)** reported feeling the most confident and connected at this year''s convention, engaging in numerous meetings with prospects, partners, and payroll companies, which led to **a contract already sent out** (00:14).  \n    - This increased networking aligned with strategic goals to build stronger industry relationships.  \n    - The positive sentiment suggests upcoming sales opportunities, though direct sales impact remains uncertain.  \n    - Confidence and familiarity with the marketplace were key factors in this progress.  \n    - This networking momentum supports longer-term pipeline development and partner collaborations.\n\n## **Website Development and Quality Control**\n\nThe website migration is underway with a focus on seamless transfer and quality assurance to support scalable content growth.\n\n- **Baylee Gunnell** and **Will Fleming** confirmed that several pages are built on a staging site, with a **quality control phase** targeting button functionality and visual consistency before final review by the client (03:14).  \n    - A tool called **Bug Herd** will enable real-time client feedback for any adjustments before launch.  \n    - The new platform removes previous page limits, allowing for more flexible content expansion.  \n    - This phased approach reduces risk of errors and enhances user experience upon launch.  \n    - The transition is expected to improve site management and support marketing efforts.\n\n## **Content Strategy and Messaging Refinement**\n\nContent updates are focused on refreshing underperforming pages and developing messaging that resonates with business owners without alienating CFOs.\n\n- The team is refreshing a landing page showing a recent **downtick in engagement** and plans to update WordPress content post-launch (05:20).  \n    - Proposed content ideas include a **30-day CFO assessment** and a **case study highlighting EBITDA improvement**, with emphasis on owner-focused messaging (10:22).  \n    - **Will Fleming** advised avoiding messaging that directly challenges CFO roles, suggesting the focus be on how services provide **financial clarity and relieve burden** rather than replacing CFOs (08:30, 21:49).  \n    - The case study was favored as a trust-building tool showing tangible results and market relevance (18:13, 29:12).  \n    - The messaging aims to help owners envision growth and success without needing deep CFO knowledge.\n\n## **ABM Campaign Targeting and Personalization**\n\nThe account-based marketing (ABM) strategy will target owners and CEOs with tailored messaging designed to build trust and encourage engagement.\n\n- A **new contact list** focusing on owners and CEOs was created to align outreach with decision-makers, with campaign content emphasizing value over free offers to drive 15-minute calls with Nick (14:35).  \n    - Messaging will delicately address issues like financial clarity and accountability without directly questioning existing CFO or controller roles (15:28, 16:36).  \n    - Splitting campaigns based on whether companies have CFOs was considered but deemed potentially inefficient; instead, a unified approach focusing on owners'' perspectives was preferred (24:38, 25:44).  \n    - **Will Fleming** stressed that all messages must go to owners/CEOs, as they are the ultimate decision-makers (26:07).  \n    - Personalization will leverage industry news, company activity, and labor market data to identify high-value targets (27:17).\n\n## **Strategic Positioning and Market Insight**\n\nThe team is aligning messaging and product positioning to address current market challenges and owner priorities amid shifting industry dynamics.\n\n- **Will Fleming** highlighted the importance of showing credibility and trust quickly, especially given downturns in growth and volume pressures in the restaurant sector (29:20).  \n    - Case studies are positioned to demonstrate how the service alleviates owners’ burdens, allowing them to focus on growth without financial worry (20:04, 30:05).  \n    - Messaging will avoid criticizing owners’ gut instincts while promoting data-driven decisions and financial clarity as a growth foundation (29:43).  \n    - The deal with a California group underscores the value of trust and credibility in closing agreements (30:20).  \n    - This approach intends to differentiate the service by focusing on results and relief rather than technical CFO tasks.\n\n## **Operational and Collaboration Enhancements**\n\nThe team is improving collaboration and content development processes to accelerate delivery and maintain quality.\n\n- **Baylee Gunnell** introduced **Guillermo**, a technical marketer brought in to support ABM efforts and backend operations, enhancing capacity without changing account leadership (01:31).  \n    - Plans include interviewing **Will Fleming** to capture expert insights for upcoming articles, ensuring authentic and impactful content (12:39).  \n    - Messaging drafts will be updated collaboratively and shared for review before launch to maintain alignment (31:03).  \n    - The use of tools like Bug Herd streamlines client feedback and reduces turnaround times for site adjustments (03:14).  \n    - These process improvements aim to increase responsiveness and content relevance while supporting scalable marketing efforts.","outline":null,"keywords":["conference networking","website redevelopment","content strategy","CFO services","ABM campaign","owner engagement"],"overview":"- **Conference Success:** Team gained industry connections, leading to a contract sent out and potential sales opportunities.  \n- **Website Migration:** Pages are built on a staging site, focused on quality control and enhanced user experience.  \n- **Content Strategy:** Updating underperforming pages to resonate with owners while ensuring CFOs are not alienated.  \n- **ABM Campaign:** Targeting owners/CEOs with personalized messaging to drive engagement and trust, avoiding CFO challenges.  \n- **Market Positioning:** Emphasizing financial clarity for owners while showcasing service benefits through credible case studies.  \n- **Operational Enhancements:** Improving collaboration and processes for faster delivery and client-centric content development.","action_items":"\n**Baylee Gunnell**\nSchedule an interview with Will Fleming to develop article content on the 30-day CFO assessment and other topics (12:39)\nSend link for Bug Herd tool invite and instructions to Will Fleming and Nick for website feedback (03:14)\nProceed with website build completion and conduct initial quality control (03:14)\nUpdate and refresh landing pages and content per Paula’s optimizations once the new WordPress site goes live (05:20)\nRefine ABM email campaign messaging targeting owners and CEOs, removing overt references to mistrust in CFOs, based on meeting input (15:44)\nDevelop and send updated email messaging concepts for review by Will Fleming and Nick S (31:03)\n\n**Will Fleming**\nProvide input and feedback on content topics, especially the 30-day CFO assessment article (12:39)\nCollaborate on drafting content for articles and ABM messaging (12:39)\n\n**Nick S (GSS)**\nSubmit headshot and podcast materials for marketing use (02:34)\nReview and provide feedback on ABM list and messaging drafts targeting owners/CEOs (14:50)\n"},"duration":31.579999923706055,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Will Fleming"},{"id":1,"name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"id":2,"name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"id":3,"name":"Will Fleming"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Was a good conference.","index":0,"end_time":0.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.16,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Nick was busy.","index":1,"end_time":1.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"More busier than me.","index":2,"end_time":3.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1.84,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Were.","index":3,"end_time":7.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":6.88,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Were you busy with a lot of those, like, meetings you had scheduled through those emails or was there something else?","index":4,"end_time":13.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":7.44,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, combination.","index":5,"end_time":15.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":14.08,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"It was that and just industry networking.","index":6,"end_time":18.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":15.28,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Okay.","index":7,"end_time":19.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":19.04,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"A lot of cocktail happy hours, dinners, prospect meetings and yeah.","index":8,"end_time":27.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":20.24,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Partner meetings.","index":9,"end_time":28.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":27.48,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Met with a couple payroll companies and yeah.","index":10,"end_time":32.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":28.68,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Trying to figure some.","index":11,"end_time":33.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":32.76,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Some things out.","index":12,"end_time":34.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":33.72,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"So, yeah, I thought it was.","index":13,"end_time":38.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":35.16,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I felt the most confident this year at that convention and the most connected.","index":14,"end_time":44.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":39.56,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"That doesn''t mean it''s going to turn into direct sales, but I just felt like I found my place at that show.","index":15,"end_time":52.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":45.16,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":16,"end_time":53.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":52.78,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I was just kind of walking around and you just knew so many people and kind of know our role there and what our goal and intentions are.","index":17,"end_time":62.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":53.58,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"And I walked around confidently knowing that.","index":18,"end_time":65.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":62.94,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"So that was a good feeling.","index":19,"end_time":66.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":65.14,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"That was a good feeling.","index":20,"end_time":67.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":66.38,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It makes a difference when you know people.","index":21,"end_time":70.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":68.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Whereas you go there and you''re like, okay, how do I.","index":22,"end_time":73.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":71.1,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You don''t know anyone.","index":23,"end_time":75.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":74.62,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Right.","index":24,"end_time":76.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":76.3,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That''s great.","index":25,"end_time":79.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":78.87,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, awesome.","index":26,"end_time":80.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":79.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You''ve already got a contract sent out.","index":27,"end_time":81.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":80.27,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Hopefully more.","index":28,"end_time":83.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":81.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"More to come there too, but sounds like it was a successful conference.","index":29,"end_time":89.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":83.75,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":30,"end_time":90.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89.75,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Well, I also want to introduce you to a new face.","index":31,"end_time":95.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":91.75,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This is Guillermo.","index":32,"end_time":97.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":95.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"She is a super talented, I would say like technical marketer.","index":33,"end_time":102.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":97.27,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So where we have this ABM running, I''m pulling her in for additional support.","index":34,"end_time":108.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":102.47,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"She''s been helping on the back end for a couple things.","index":35,"end_time":111.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":108.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m still going to be on your account.","index":36,"end_time":113.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":112.11,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m the account director on your account, so I''m not going anywhere.","index":37,"end_time":116.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":113.47,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But GA is just here to support.","index":38,"end_time":119.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":116.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yep.","index":39,"end_time":120.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":120.349,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Nice meeting you guys.","index":40,"end_time":121.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":120.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Nice meeting you.","index":41,"end_time":123.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":122.43,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yep.","index":42,"end_time":125.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":124.99,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Great.","index":43,"end_time":126.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":126.19,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, we''ll go ahead and get into our agenda.","index":44,"end_time":130.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":126.59,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we''re going to go over some website updates, your content updates, and then we''ll definitely want to talk through some ABM updates here.","index":45,"end_time":143.519,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":133.759,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Lots of things going on there and we''ve got several ideas and just things we want to run by yet, but anything else you all want to chat through today?","index":46,"end_time":151.519,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":143.679,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Just one quick update.","index":47,"end_time":156.159,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":154.879,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I finally got the headshot from my last podcast.","index":48,"end_time":159.759,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":156.799,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I mean, she was at the convention and she had to get something from her marketing department.","index":49,"end_time":164.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":160.04,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"So I will submit all that information today for the podcast that was recorded a week or so ago.","index":50,"end_time":171.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":164.6,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Oh, awesome.","index":51,"end_time":172.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":171.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, so that it''s.","index":52,"end_time":174.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":172.44,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"The.","index":53,"end_time":174.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":174.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"The video is saved in Riverside and all that stuff.","index":54,"end_time":178.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":174.4,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Don''t know if you saw it, but then we''ll.","index":55,"end_time":181.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":178.92,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I''ll get you all the coordinated or all the information to you.","index":56,"end_time":185.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":181.96,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":57,"end_time":186.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":186.74,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, we can just pull it from reverse side and yeah, thanks for getting that headshot.","index":58,"end_time":191.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":186.98,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That Definitely helps.","index":59,"end_time":192.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":191.3,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":60,"end_time":193.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":192.74,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay, so starting with the website, Will and I, we did talk about this last week, but this is actually currently underway.","index":61,"end_time":203.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":194.9,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we''ve already built out a couple pages on a staging site.","index":62,"end_time":209.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":204.26,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So Guille and I, we''re gonna do a round of.","index":63,"end_time":214.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":209.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, we''re first going to get everything built out.","index":64,"end_time":217.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":214.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll go through and do some quality control first.","index":65,"end_time":219.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":217.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"When you''re transferring a whole website, like, sometimes little things get missed.","index":66,"end_time":224.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":220.17,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we''ll, we''ll go through all the buttons, make sure those are working correctly, and then we''ll send it over to you to do a final review as well.","index":67,"end_time":232.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":224.05,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And I do.","index":68,"end_time":234.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":233.05,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Let me grab the link and I''ll just show you.","index":69,"end_time":236.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":234.73,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''re going to use a tool called Bug Herd to put in any feedback.","index":70,"end_time":242.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":236.81,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Let me grab the link real quick.","index":71,"end_time":246.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":244.11,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":72,"end_time":253.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":252.75,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So you should get an invite from us.","index":73,"end_time":257.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":254.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It might not be showing up for me right now.","index":74,"end_time":262.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":260.19,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I''ll just show you on a different website how this works.","index":75,"end_time":264.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":262.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But you''ll have this little pop up over here and if there''s like anything you want us to adjust, you''ll just hit this, like, tag and element and then you can leave feedback.","index":76,"end_time":275.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":265.77,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So you''re like, if you wanted to make any changes, I don''t imagine we''re going to have anything too crazy, but you could be like, please change this image or the spacing here looks weird, or whatever comment you have on things you want us to adjust, and then that''ll come to our team and we''ll make those adjustments before we go live.","index":77,"end_time":295.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":275.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But like, so here it is.","index":78,"end_time":298.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.85,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, we''ve already built out a lot of stuff and it''s looking, I mean, pretty identical to what you have already on Duda.","index":79,"end_time":305.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":298.33,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But yeah, super excited for this.","index":80,"end_time":308.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":306.25,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think it''ll, it''ll help us a lot and won''t have a limit on the number of pages we can create.","index":81,"end_time":314.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":308.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But do you have any questions on this?","index":82,"end_time":316.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":314.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I don''t, I don''t.","index":83,"end_time":320.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":319.62,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":84,"end_time":322.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":320.82,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So then next we have a couple of content updates we were able to refresh or work.","index":85,"end_time":334.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":324.74,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think we''re currently working on this landing page refresh.","index":86,"end_time":337.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":334.14,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That was from our, like, content meeting we had a couple weeks ago.","index":87,"end_time":342.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":338.66,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It was one we noticed had a little bit of a downtick.","index":88,"end_time":344.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":342.22,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we''re working through that right now.","index":89,"end_time":346.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":344.9,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then you saw these optimizations from Paula about last week.","index":90,"end_time":352.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":346.89,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So once we get the new WordPress website live, we''ll go ahead and get these updated as well.","index":91,"end_time":358.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":352.89,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then we have some new topic ideas that we wanted to run by you.","index":92,"end_time":366.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":359.45,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So there''s A lot here too.","index":93,"end_time":369.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":367.13,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think this is a good opportunity.","index":94,"end_time":372.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":371.13,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll probably want to pick maybe two to tackle this next month.","index":95,"end_time":376.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":372.89,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But, like, just out of first glance, are any of these standing out to you?","index":96,"end_time":382.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":378.69,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Are there any of these that you feel like aren''t very relevant anymore and then we can just go from there?","index":97,"end_time":390.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":382.69,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Some of these we''ve done in some capacity over time.","index":98,"end_time":411.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":408.22,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I would like to see what you had in mind for the CFO services.","index":99,"end_time":417.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":413.34,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"ROI calculator.","index":100,"end_time":418.699,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":417.34,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Yeah, this would be cool.","index":101,"end_time":420.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":419.66,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I don''t know what Will thinks about that, but I don''t know kind of what metrics you would pull there.","index":102,"end_time":427.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":422.54,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"That''S.","index":103,"end_time":429.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":429.51,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Obviously going to engage maybe ownership groups and PE groups per se, but the CFOs are going to probably rip that up pretty quickly.","index":104,"end_time":442.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":429.79,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Is there something like when you''re onboarding someone to do this, do you run any calculations on this or have any rough numbers of, like, here''s your expected roi?","index":105,"end_time":460.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":445.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I mean, for myself, being, you know, newer to CFO services per se, all we''ve done is we knew what the budget of one of our clients was to get a new CFO on board, and then what we are charging them.","index":106,"end_time":477.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":462.66,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"And.","index":107,"end_time":478.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":477.86,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"We just did, you know, hey, we''re saving this guy how much per month or how much per year and payroll and benefits.","index":108,"end_time":488.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":480.26,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"The only problem here is that that piece goes out to a huge audience.","index":109,"end_time":498.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":489.76,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Some of them are customers.","index":110,"end_time":499.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":498.24,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And if I was working with us and I was a CFO and I.","index":111,"end_time":505.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":499.6,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Received this, it wouldn''t make me feel good about tss.","index":112,"end_time":509.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":505.64,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Right.","index":113,"end_time":510.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":510.48,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s what I was thinking.","index":114,"end_time":512.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":510.84,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"So I don''t think I want to.","index":115,"end_time":514.909,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":513.389,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Be that direct and be that hostile.","index":116,"end_time":519.389,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.909,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":117,"end_time":520.509,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":520.029,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Could we position it in a way that it''s like not meant to replace the cfo.","index":118,"end_time":527.349,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":521.629,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''s more like using these services are going to help you with your cash flow.","index":119,"end_time":534.789,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":527.349,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''s going to help you with xyz.","index":120,"end_time":537.149,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":534.789,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But are we still.","index":121,"end_time":539.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":538.12,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Then that would just fall to the other.","index":122,"end_time":542.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":540.44,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That would fall to one of these other categories because it would be more general.","index":123,"end_time":545.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":542.84,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah, we just get these.","index":124,"end_time":548.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":546.28,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"These scenarios where we''re talking about somebody''s.","index":125,"end_time":551.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":549,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Job which is more geared towards the role.","index":126,"end_time":554.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":551.44,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"We need to be careful.","index":127,"end_time":557.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":555.24,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So I wouldn''t want to send out.","index":128,"end_time":561.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":559.56,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"A newsletter about the return.","index":129,"end_time":563.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":561.28,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Return on investment of a position of any business.","index":130,"end_time":567.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":563.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, when you talk generally about.","index":131,"end_time":569.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":567.96,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Outsourcing and the return on outsourcing and you compare the cost, I mean, it gets into some of that, but I don''t think it''s a good idea to target people''s positions.","index":132,"end_time":581.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":569.92,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":133,"end_time":582.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":581.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So with that said, Will, don''t we have already something about like a case study on Munson?","index":134,"end_time":591.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":584.36,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Wouldn''t that be the EBITDA improvement playbook?","index":135,"end_time":594.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":591.25,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Okay, that''s kind of.","index":136,"end_time":596.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":594.69,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I think this one too.","index":137,"end_time":599.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":597.65,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think these were just like different angles we could take with them, but we can.","index":138,"end_time":604.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":599.41,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, this one too was a different angle.","index":139,"end_time":607.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":605.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we can get.","index":140,"end_time":609.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":608.61,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ll just get rid of these ones, if that''s okay.","index":141,"end_time":611.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":609.49,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":142,"end_time":615.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":615.42,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Any of these other ones standing out?","index":143,"end_time":619.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":617.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I mean, I think that the 30 day CFO assessment, what to expect, might be a good follow up to what.","index":144,"end_time":628.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":622.14,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"We''Re going out for.","index":145,"end_time":630.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":628.38,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, but that would be people.","index":146,"end_time":632.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":630.54,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That haven''t, people that haven''t received it.","index":147,"end_time":634.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":632.34,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"We could talk about how we''re trying to bring some standardization to this area.","index":148,"end_time":642.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":635.02,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But not, you know, the, you know.","index":149,"end_time":645.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":642.14,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Not so much talk about replacing the CFO as, or questioning that, but just it''s like our take on senior financial.","index":150,"end_time":656.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":646.01,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Tasks, how they should, how, how to think about and what to focus on.","index":151,"end_time":663.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":657.29,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And then at the end say that hey, we, we''ve got a 30 day assessment that''s popular with owners or something like that that we can help provide.","index":152,"end_time":675.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":665.21,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, that one and then I kind of like the next one, you know, 10, 30, 50, just for.","index":153,"end_time":687.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":676.41,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It helps people think because they don''t.","index":154,"end_time":689.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":687.13,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Really know.","index":155,"end_time":689.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":689.13,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"How it grows, how the, you know, what''s, what''s the role?","index":156,"end_time":697.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":691.53,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And.","index":157,"end_time":697.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":697.13,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah, I think different approaches you have to take.","index":158,"end_time":702.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":699.46,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"What do they, what should they be thinking about looking forward to the future?","index":159,"end_time":707.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":703.22,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Well, because I mean, I think when, I mean the people start, it''s always hard.","index":160,"end_time":716.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":708.02,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Like it''s always harder than you think.","index":161,"end_time":718.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":716.54,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It is when you''re building a business.","index":162,"end_time":719.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":718.14,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But I think what gets people excited.","index":163,"end_time":722.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":720.26,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And the reason they, they''re starting the business in the first place is because.","index":164,"end_time":725.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":722.1,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"They have in their mind a happy.","index":165,"end_time":728.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":725.78,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Place that is more growth and more success.","index":166,"end_time":731.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":728.62,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So if we talk about that and take away some of the gray of this area towards when they''re 30, 40, 50, I think that that''s a positive picture that we can paint.","index":167,"end_time":750.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":733.1,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And so we bill help, you know, in their mind, maybe solidify part of a plan for the future that makes them happy.","index":168,"end_time":758.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":750.94,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s a great idea.","index":169,"end_time":761.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":759.37,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, let''s kind of like what we''ve done before.","index":170,"end_time":765.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":762.89,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think it''d be great if we could hop on a call and we''ll, we''ll interview you to get your take on that.","index":171,"end_time":770.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":765.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I''ll, I''ll send over a link and we can get that scheduled for later this week or early next week.","index":172,"end_time":775.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":770.57,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Just a Quick question on this, like what to expect?","index":173,"end_time":779.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":776.41,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is this something okay that, that you''re okay for the general public to see?","index":174,"end_time":785.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":780.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Because right now we''ve been like just using our specific ABM audience.","index":175,"end_time":790.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":785.41,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is it okay with you if like everyone else sees that you''re doing a 30 day offer?","index":176,"end_time":795.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":790.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''s, it''s just up to you.","index":177,"end_time":797.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":796.13,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I can help, I can help write it like, or like you can, you can sort of lead.","index":178,"end_time":803.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":797.65,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I can help you sort of do it.","index":179,"end_time":807.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":806.22,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah, you can start it.","index":180,"end_time":808.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":807.86,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I''ll have some opinions.","index":181,"end_time":810.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":808.94,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay, so I''m gonna take a quick.","index":182,"end_time":812.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":810.02,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Call, I need to take a call from a customer.","index":183,"end_time":814.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":812.38,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":184,"end_time":816.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":814.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do what you gotta do.","index":185,"end_time":818.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":817.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, well we''ll get started on these two articles then I''ll just go ahead and change these to topic approved.","index":186,"end_time":827.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":819.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We will get started talking about some of the ABM stuff but we''ll, we''ll probably back.","index":187,"end_time":838.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":834.12,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But I''d love your thoughts on a few things.","index":188,"end_time":840.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":838.88,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Nick.","index":189,"end_time":842.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":841.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we got your email and your Will''s email about wanting to focus on the owner and CEO.","index":190,"end_time":850.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":842.6,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we created a new list.","index":191,"end_time":852.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":850.76,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"All the same companies, just different titles.","index":192,"end_time":857.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":852.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So that''s what we''re going to do for this next campaign, focusing on these people.","index":193,"end_time":862.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":857.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll send it over to you to take a look out to before we go ahead and launch.","index":194,"end_time":867.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":862.44,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then we wanted to get your feedback on some messaging.","index":195,"end_time":874.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":869.06,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"One of the things Will had mentioned is not putting so much of a focus on that it''s a free offer initially and leading with other value.","index":196,"end_time":885.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":875.22,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like it sounds like we want the main goal for them to be to get on a 15 minute conversation with you and then from there you can kind of pitch that idea, build some trust.","index":197,"end_time":895.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":885.14,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So Guy and I put together a couple of ideas of like different email topics because we still should have like an angle or like some sort of value we''re adding.","index":198,"end_time":909.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":897.08,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But we wanted to get your thoughts on a few things.","index":199,"end_time":912.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":909.8,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like one of the things Will had mentioned is that owners, some are maybe not sure if they trust the controller or the cfo, but that was one thing I was like, are we going like, is that maybe a hurtful message?","index":200,"end_time":928.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":912.68,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like how can we approach that in a tactful way?","index":201,"end_time":931.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":928.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I''m not sure if that''s like territory we should avoid in emails.","index":202,"end_time":936.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":932.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And that''s just something you talk about with them in the call.","index":203,"end_time":939.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":936.73,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So that''s one thing I wanted to get your thoughts on.","index":204,"end_time":941.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":940.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then we''ve got other ideas as well.","index":205,"end_time":943.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":941.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, it''s funny, bring that up.","index":206,"end_time":945.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.42,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"One of the big drivers of how we are going to land this chicken concept is he said at dinner he doesn''t trust his controller, which was shocking for an owner to say just out front.","index":207,"end_time":960.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":946.66,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"But.","index":208,"end_time":961.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":960.82,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, if you can delicately do it, you know, maybe say, are you holding them to the right accountability metrics or maybe do you trust your controller or your cfo?","index":209,"end_time":974.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":963.14,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"That''s.","index":210,"end_time":975.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":974.62,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That''s a little brash.","index":211,"end_time":976.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":975.06,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":212,"end_time":977.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":976.78,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But kind of word it delicately saying, you know, hey, are they doing the right things?","index":213,"end_time":982.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":977.58,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"And do you feel comfortable with what''s going on?","index":214,"end_time":987.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":983.34,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I think that''ll be a good idea because those are the things.","index":215,"end_time":992.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":989.42,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I mean, being a former owner, those are the things you think about.","index":216,"end_time":996.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":993.26,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Right?","index":217,"end_time":996.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":996.65,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Those are the things you''re always constantly, you know, are people doing the right thing at the right time?","index":218,"end_time":1002.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":996.81,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Not.","index":219,"end_time":1003.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1002.81,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Not a level of trust, but, you know, am I getting the right stuff?","index":220,"end_time":1007.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1003.17,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Are they doing the right thing?","index":221,"end_time":1008.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1007.21,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"You''re not thinking that they''re stealing or they''re purposely doing things wrong.","index":222,"end_time":1013.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1009.61,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"But if we can angle it that way, I think that''ll be good.","index":223,"end_time":1018.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1015.69,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":224,"end_time":1019.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1019.13,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":225,"end_time":1020.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1020.41,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I like that.","index":226,"end_time":1021.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1020.89,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And maybe even it could like tie into this first one here is like, do you feel like you have financial clarity?","index":227,"end_time":1029.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1021.45,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is that coming from your controller or cfo?","index":228,"end_time":1033.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1030.24,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Maybe those two things could tie in.","index":229,"end_time":1036.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1034.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I like that.","index":230,"end_time":1038.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1037.12,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":231,"end_time":1038.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1038.32,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Okay.","index":232,"end_time":1039.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1039.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well.","index":233,"end_time":1041.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.36,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You doing okay, Will?","index":234,"end_time":1044.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1043.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is your call.","index":235,"end_time":1045.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1044.88,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m back.","index":236,"end_time":1046.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1045.6,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Sorry about that.","index":237,"end_time":1047.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1046.56,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I.","index":238,"end_time":1047.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1047.36,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That was a call.","index":239,"end_time":1048.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1047.6,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I couldn''t.","index":240,"end_time":1049.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1048.36,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It''s all good then.","index":241,"end_time":1052.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1050.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I.","index":242,"end_time":1052.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1052.44,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Did I miss something?","index":243,"end_time":1053.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1053,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"We were just talking about ideas for this next email sequence, so Guy and I put together a few different angles.","index":244,"end_time":1064.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1054.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we just want to get your thoughts on like, which ones.","index":245,"end_time":1067.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1065.08,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Which of these ideas you feel like would really resonate or if you have any other like additional thoughts on how we can position these.","index":246,"end_time":1076.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1067.88,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Because we don''t want to lead with the free assessment.","index":247,"end_time":1078.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1076.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So just kind of changing the angle a bit to lead with some value in a different angle to get them on a 15 minute call with Nick.","index":248,"end_time":1086.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1079.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I guess if.","index":249,"end_time":1096.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1093.92,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I guess the case study is the.","index":250,"end_time":1101.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1099.28,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Is makes.","index":251,"end_time":1103.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1102.64,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Feels like right.","index":252,"end_time":1107.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1103.76,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I guess I just, I think like, if the.","index":253,"end_time":1112.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1107.77,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"The.","index":254,"end_time":1112.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1112.33,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"For us to have to make traction with in this process, we need to make sure that we''re connecting with the owner.","index":255,"end_time":1123.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1113.25,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yes.","index":256,"end_time":1124.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1124.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":257,"end_time":1125.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1125.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And so like, can you go back to that slide just for a second?","index":258,"end_time":1129.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1125.45,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":259,"end_time":1130.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1129.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You don''t mind?","index":260,"end_time":1131.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1130.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So like, I, I just, I kind of think some.","index":261,"end_time":1136.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1131.44,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I think we have to be careful.","index":262,"end_time":1139.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1136.8,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Like, like pretty quickly you can see some of these things, like you''re actually getting like.","index":263,"end_time":1147.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1139.6,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Let''s just say you have an owner that''s sitting in the company and he, he''s not feeling great about his CFO.","index":264,"end_time":1153.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1147.8,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Or he doesn''t even have one and.","index":265,"end_time":1156.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1153.48,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"He''S not going to be the cfo.","index":266,"end_time":1157.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1156.04,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Like the financial clarity.","index":267,"end_time":1159.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1157.92,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay.","index":268,"end_time":1161.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1160.8,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But they''re kind of expecting that that''s going to be sort of like spoon fed to them from a cfo.","index":269,"end_time":1169.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1161.92,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Like some of these other things are like getting into the actual job.","index":270,"end_time":1172.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1169.44,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Whereas like from the owner''s perspective, like a case study, it''s like, yeah, I could see myself, I want to be 50.","index":271,"end_time":1179.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1173.28,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It looks like these guys have did a lot of help or.","index":272,"end_time":1182.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1179.28,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean bandwidth, I think that''s like you''re, it''s.","index":273,"end_time":1190.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1186.24,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"They look at that and they might think I mean it.","index":274,"end_time":1195.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1190.8,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean he''s not.","index":275,"end_time":1196.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1195.6,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"The owner''s not the CFO today, so he doesn''t have a bandwidth issue because he''s not doing it.","index":276,"end_time":1201.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1196.44,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I don''t know if that''s relevant.","index":277,"end_time":1203.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1202.24,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay.","index":278,"end_time":1204.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1204.08,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"The other one, the hidden cost, I mean I understand they could look at that and say okay, that could be us.","index":279,"end_time":1211.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1206.16,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But I don''t think they think about reporting so much.","index":280,"end_time":1215.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1211.76,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I think ultimately it''s, I mean financial clarity is a foundation of growth.","index":281,"end_time":1221.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1216.84,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But it''s like ultimately they want to.","index":282,"end_time":1225.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1221.24,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Know.","index":283,"end_time":1225.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1225.32,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That they''re going in the right direction, I guess.","index":284,"end_time":1231.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1227.8,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Clarity, but it''s more like trust I imagine.","index":285,"end_time":1236.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1231.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Like so my mother in law, it.","index":286,"end_time":1239.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1236.88,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Sometimes is really afraid about financial things so she ends up not buying a.","index":287,"end_time":1245.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1239.89,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Cup of star like a, just like, oh, I''m not going to go to Starbucks.","index":288,"end_time":1248.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1245.29,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s like if you went to Starbucks 10 times every day for like.","index":289,"end_time":1253.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1248.93,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Three months probably wouldn''t make a difference.","index":290,"end_time":1255.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1253.13,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But it''s just like, it''s like the knowledge, it''s like, you know, it''s done, it''s covered and they can, they can do things without having to be concerned all the time.","index":291,"end_time":1267.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1257.17,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So it''s like I look at the case study is taking a huge burden off of somebody''s desk and helping them.","index":292,"end_time":1278.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1267.75,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And allowing them to attach to the business that they''re not in a way that they''re not.","index":293,"end_time":1284.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1279.39,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That''s easy for them.","index":294,"end_time":1286.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1284.83,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But it''s like before we showed up.","index":295,"end_time":1288.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1286.07,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"They weren''t comfortable to do that.","index":296,"end_time":1289.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1288.55,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That''s what happened in the case study.","index":297,"end_time":1291.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1289.79,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And so I think that we have to sort of like, hey, these things are all going to be tidied up and it''s going to be kind of.","index":298,"end_time":1300.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1292.17,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yes, no questions, check the box approach to the financial area of the company.","index":299,"end_time":1305.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1300.53,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"As opposed to you having to learn something new.","index":300,"end_time":1309.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1305.53,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":301,"end_time":1310.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1309.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"There''s probably a few ways we could position the case Study, too, that might help them relate.","index":302,"end_time":1316.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1311.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, are you trying to grow to a certain number of units?","index":303,"end_time":1319.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1316.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, have you had challenges maybe getting financing from a bank?","index":304,"end_time":1323.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1320.5,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Because there were, like, several challenges that this case study had that might be relatable to the owners.","index":305,"end_time":1331.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1323.78,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":306,"end_time":1332.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1332.42,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And I think that some of the basics is just like, are you forecasting your prime costs?","index":307,"end_time":1338.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1332.82,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"You know, do you.","index":308,"end_time":1339.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1338.9,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Do you know?","index":309,"end_time":1340.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1339.7,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But it''s not clarity, necessarily.","index":310,"end_time":1342.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1340.66,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It''s just, are you doing these things?","index":311,"end_time":1345.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1342.86,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And then focus on, if we do these things, there''s results.","index":312,"end_time":1349.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1346.27,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So, like, I just.","index":313,"end_time":1353.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1350.83,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I think some of these, when I read them, it''s like we''re trying to make it more comfortable for the owner to slide into the shoes of the cfo.","index":314,"end_time":1362.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1353.39,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And that''s not, in my mind, what we want to do is provide information that allows them to believe that we''re.","index":315,"end_time":1371.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1363.23,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Just going to cover it for them.","index":316,"end_time":1373.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1371.83,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":317,"end_time":1374.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1373.71,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Supposed to kind of make the CFO information easier.","index":318,"end_time":1378.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1374.59,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"No, it''s like they don''t even want to be exposed to it if they don''t have to.","index":319,"end_time":1382.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1378.19,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"They want the results without the work.","index":320,"end_time":1385.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1383.23,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Do you think it''s different if they have a CFO versus if they don''t have one?","index":321,"end_time":1393.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1388.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I do.","index":322,"end_time":1396.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1395.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Because if they.","index":323,"end_time":1396.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1396.16,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Well, no, I don''t think it''s that much different.","index":324,"end_time":1398.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1396.96,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I think if they have one and things aren''t working, they''re like, I don''t know what he does.","index":325,"end_time":1402.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1398.92,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay.","index":326,"end_time":1403.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1402.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I know it''s not right.","index":327,"end_time":1404.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1403.48,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It''s.","index":328,"end_time":1406.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.28,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It''s kind of like that old saying about pornography.","index":329,"end_time":1409.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1406.76,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It''s like, I don''t really know what it looks like, but if I saw.","index":330,"end_time":1412.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1409.4,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It, I''d know what I''m looking at.","index":331,"end_time":1414.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1412.16,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay.","index":332,"end_time":1415.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1414.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''s like, I don''t know what that''s supposed to look like, but I know that it doesn''t look like what that guy''s doing.","index":333,"end_time":1423.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1415.8,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":334,"end_time":1423.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1423.33,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":335,"end_time":1424.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1423.81,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And so if we could present ourselves as.","index":336,"end_time":1426.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1424.33,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"As a.","index":337,"end_time":1427.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.77,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Sort of.","index":338,"end_time":1428.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1427.61,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"As a standard.","index":339,"end_time":1430.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1428.85,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It''s like these guys seem like they.","index":340,"end_time":1431.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1430.17,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Know what they''re talking about, and I know that guy doesn''t, so I''m going to at least talk to them.","index":341,"end_time":1435.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1431.61,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay.","index":342,"end_time":1436.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1436.05,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So this might get us into some personalized ideas.","index":343,"end_time":1441.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1437.25,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This is something we''ve been talking about a lot.","index":344,"end_time":1443.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1441.65,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I almost wonder if we could split the campaign, like, our list of people into companies that have a cfo, and then they can get that messaging about, like, are you.","index":345,"end_time":1456.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1443.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Are.","index":346,"end_time":1457.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1456.82,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do you feel comfortable?","index":347,"end_time":1458.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1457.1,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, do you know what''s going on?","index":348,"end_time":1459.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1458.1,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And, like, be sensitive kind of about that messaging?","index":349,"end_time":1462.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1460.38,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then people who don''t have a cfo, they could have something, maybe a Little different about, like, what you were saying.","index":350,"end_time":1471.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1463.18,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m having a hard time repeating exactly what it was.","index":351,"end_time":1473.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1471.02,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But what.","index":352,"end_time":1474.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1473.42,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"What are.","index":353,"end_time":1474.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1474.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"What are your thoughts?","index":354,"end_time":1475.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1474.76,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, do you feel like that would be maybe a good way to split them?","index":355,"end_time":1478.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1475.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"If you''re able to do that, if you''re able to be that.","index":356,"end_time":1481.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1478.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That refined?","index":357,"end_time":1482.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1481.6,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I think.","index":358,"end_time":1483.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1482.56,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, there''s definitely a guy that''s out there with 10 locations.","index":359,"end_time":1487.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1483.28,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"He wants to be 20, and he''s thinking that, you know, part one event that goes from get help, gets him from 10 to 20, is hiring a CFO.","index":360,"end_time":1496.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1487.24,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"There''s definitely a guy out there that''s like that.","index":361,"end_time":1499.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1496.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And then there''s definitely a guy out there that has 10 with, you know.","index":362,"end_time":1504.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1499.6,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Fractional CFO or even a CFO.","index":363,"end_time":1506.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1504.15,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And he''s like, I don''t.","index":364,"end_time":1506.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1506.03,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That guy''s not gonna get me there.","index":365,"end_time":1508.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1506.91,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But I don''t know what to do to find somebody that is.","index":366,"end_time":1511.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1508.39,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, there.","index":367,"end_time":1512.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1511.67,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But I don''t.","index":368,"end_time":1512.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1512.35,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That seems like in the.","index":369,"end_time":1515.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1512.95,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"You''d spend a lot of time trying to figure out who has one and.","index":370,"end_time":1519.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1515.59,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Who has the other where.","index":371,"end_time":1520.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1519.15,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I don''t know if the message needs.","index":372,"end_time":1522.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1520.51,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"To be that refined.","index":373,"end_time":1523.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1522.03,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"You know what I''m saying?","index":374,"end_time":1524.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1523.83,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Like, yeah, I don''t know.","index":375,"end_time":1525.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1524.75,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Those guys are that different.","index":376,"end_time":1527.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1525.91,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I think that it''s kind of like the case study is our results.","index":377,"end_time":1537.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1533.9,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It looks very good.","index":378,"end_time":1539.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1538.46,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It looks very interesting.","index":379,"end_time":1540.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1539.54,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Can we build the trust.","index":380,"end_time":1542.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1541.5,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"In the.","index":381,"end_time":1545.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1544.86,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Way we present ourselves to validate that result?","index":382,"end_time":1549.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1545.74,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And then can we make that result attractive or at least try to touch the demand?","index":383,"end_time":1555.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1549.9,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So, like, yeah, I should talk to those guys, because they seem like they get these kind of results because I''m not getting them from what I have.","index":384,"end_time":1562.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1555.26,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So I don''t know if you need to try to break it apart for the.","index":385,"end_time":1567.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1564.41,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, one thing that''s clear, it always has to go to the CEO or the owner.","index":386,"end_time":1573.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1567.37,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":387,"end_time":1574.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1574.17,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Whether he has.","index":388,"end_time":1576.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1575.29,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, if he has a CFO and he''s happy and he''s life''s great.","index":389,"end_time":1579.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1576.33,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And he''s moving on, he''s.","index":390,"end_time":1580.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1579.13,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"He''s not a target.","index":391,"end_time":1581.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1580.41,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":392,"end_time":1582.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1581.85,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So.","index":393,"end_time":1582.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1582.49,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And then the one guy doesn''t have a cfo, he doesn''t know what to do.","index":394,"end_time":1587.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1584.25,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"The other guy has a CFO and he knows at least he''s got to get rid of that guy, but he won''t, because he doesn''t have a solution.","index":395,"end_time":1592.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1587.05,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So both of the we are solutions.","index":396,"end_time":1594.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1592.39,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Both of those scenarios.","index":397,"end_time":1595.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1594.79,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay.","index":398,"end_time":1597.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1596.55,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Nick, is there anything you''d want to add to that?","index":399,"end_time":1600.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1597.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"No, I''m good.","index":400,"end_time":1602.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1601.83,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Okay.","index":401,"end_time":1603.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1603.11,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And then, Nick, I know you had mentioned to us previously that, like, you''ve done a lot of personalization and like, research.","index":402,"end_time":1612.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1604.07,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Are there any, like, specific things that you''ve found have resonated?","index":403,"end_time":1617.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1613.43,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, certain things about the company, like, things we should be looking for.","index":404,"end_time":1623.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1618.65,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, here are a couple ideas, but like, is location something or like reviews people are leaving online?","index":405,"end_time":1630.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1623.61,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, what are some of the things that historically you''ve kept an eye out for?","index":406,"end_time":1636.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1631.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, so I always start my morning with my coffee and reading the industry publications.","index":407,"end_time":1641.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1637.37,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Okay.","index":408,"end_time":1643.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1642.65,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I subscribe to a bunch of stuff and, and I reference what we.","index":409,"end_time":1648.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1643.37,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"It''s like this restaurant finance monitor, top 200.","index":410,"end_time":1651.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1648.28,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"And I read news about them or whoever it is, and it could be anybody.","index":411,"end_time":1659.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1654.36,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Like for instance, this morning, the.","index":412,"end_time":1662.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1659.8,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"The group that owns Papa John''s and I mean thousands and thousands of locations.","index":413,"end_time":1667.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1663.8,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"They.","index":414,"end_time":1668.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1668.52,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"They''re exploring a sale or at least the valuation.","index":415,"end_time":1672.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1669.24,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Obviously that''s out of our league.","index":416,"end_time":1674.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1672.99,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"I mean, they own thousands of locations.","index":417,"end_time":1676.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1674.31,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"But just to give you an example, I would read that article and then I would say, hey, that''s a good prime target for us.","index":418,"end_time":1684.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1677.63,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Who there should we contact if I haven''t contacted them before?","index":419,"end_time":1688.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1685.23,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"And then what I do is I reference the article.","index":420,"end_time":1691.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1689.07,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":421,"end_time":1692.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1691.87,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":422,"end_time":1693.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1693.07,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"You know, I just.","index":423,"end_time":1694.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1693.43,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"And then I''ll do some more research of the company.","index":424,"end_time":1697.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1694.83,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"You know, just, you know, sound.","index":425,"end_time":1700.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1698.28,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"A.","index":426,"end_time":1704,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1703.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Little bit more intelligent and plugged into what they''re doing.","index":427,"end_time":1706.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1704,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"And then obviously the industry and then your other things here too, I reference that once in a while.","index":428,"end_time":1713.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1706.64,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"You know, if they are located in a high labor market, that''s even more intriguing.","index":429,"end_time":1717.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1713.12,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"You know, if they are buying, acquiring, selling, or whatever they''re doing, those are basically the things I look at.","index":430,"end_time":1725.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1718.76,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Okay.","index":431,"end_time":1726.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1726.08,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":432,"end_time":1728.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1728.24,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":433,"end_time":1729.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1728.76,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, that.","index":434,"end_time":1733.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1732.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That''s really helpful to know.","index":435,"end_time":1735.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1733.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Then we had two.","index":436,"end_time":1739.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1736.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Two more ideas.","index":437,"end_time":1740.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1739.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Just wanted to see what your thoughts are on this.","index":438,"end_time":1743.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1740.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do you feel like these would resonate or do we want to mostly just focus on the case study?","index":439,"end_time":1748.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1743.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I like the case study a lot because that just shows credibility.","index":440,"end_time":1755.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1752.65,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"And then it obviously references what we''re trying to do.","index":441,"end_time":1758.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1756.01,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t know if we.","index":442,"end_time":1761.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1760.73,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"If you''re going to get a lot of takers about the first one.","index":443,"end_time":1765.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1761.81,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Growth.","index":444,"end_time":1765.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1765.37,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, volumes are down.","index":445,"end_time":1767.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1765.85,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Everybody kind of knows that.","index":446,"end_time":1768.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1767.21,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, there''s some people that are doing okay, but I mean, growth is.","index":447,"end_time":1772.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1768.57,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"We have to be sensitive to the.","index":448,"end_time":1773.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1772.41,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Environment we''re in, which is there''s a perception that.","index":449,"end_time":1777.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1773.81,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"That the grocery stores have won the battle and people are eating at home.","index":450,"end_time":1783.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1777.46,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":451,"end_time":1784.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1783.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So.","index":452,"end_time":1784.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1784.1,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay, I don''t think.","index":453,"end_time":1789.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1787.7,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I mean, I think it''s a good idea to replace the gut feeling with data, but that''s in a way that''s.","index":454,"end_time":1797.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1789.78,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Saying that in most restaurant owners, start with the gut.","index":455,"end_time":1801.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1797.82,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"I don''t want to tell them that''s wrong.","index":456,"end_time":1803.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1802.18,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay.","index":457,"end_time":1805.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1805.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":458,"end_time":1806.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1806,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Like even if it''s better.","index":459,"end_time":1808.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1806.88,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"But it''s just, I just, I think.","index":460,"end_time":1811.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1808.2,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"It''S, it''s, it''s all about like when we, I talked to the.","index":461,"end_time":1816.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1811.76,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"So we''re going to get this agreement signed, hopefully this group from the, from the California.","index":462,"end_time":1822.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1816.56,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And it was all about their perception.","index":463,"end_time":1826.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1822.04,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"From start to finish was that we''re credible and we''ve built trust in a short period of time and that''s what.","index":464,"end_time":1839.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1826.72,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"We need to do.","index":465,"end_time":1840.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1839.62,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Like somehow if we''re in an elect.","index":466,"end_time":1843.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1840.62,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"And I think you do that with.","index":467,"end_time":1844.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1843.06,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"The case study and then I don''t.","index":468,"end_time":1848.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1844.22,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Know, just trying to associate working with.","index":469,"end_time":1851.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1848.06,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Us to giving them results through challenges that are in the market today.","index":470,"end_time":1855.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1851.1,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Low volumes, a finicky customer, things like that.","index":471,"end_time":1861.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1855.5,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay, that''s great.","index":472,"end_time":1864.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1863.23,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I know we''re a little over time now.","index":473,"end_time":1866.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1864.19,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":474,"end_time":1867.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1866.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This brought a lot of clarity.","index":475,"end_time":1868.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1867.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I love hearing the insights that you''re having like at the conferences and I think that''ll help us refine the messaging a lot.","index":476,"end_time":1876.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1869.39,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So Guy and I, we''re going to work on updating that messaging and we''ll send it over to you to review once it''s ready.","index":477,"end_time":1884.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1876.27,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Great.","index":478,"end_time":1885.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1885.24,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay, thank you.","index":479,"end_time":1886.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1885.6,"speaker_name":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":480,"end_time":1886.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1886.4,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Okay, we''ll see you.","index":481,"end_time":1888.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1886.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Bye.","index":482,"end_time":1888.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1888.44,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"},{"text":"Bye.","index":483,"end_time":1889.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1888.76,"speaker_name":"Will Fleming"}],"dateString":"2025-11-19T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83236942727?pwd=NaLGKm3JEGM6umJeSVS9pHPmDfNAYN.1","participants":["baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,guille.santana@marketersindemand.com,nstauff@gsslp.com,wfleming@gsslp.com","guille.santana@marketersindemand.com","nstauff@gsslp.com","wfleming@gsslp.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01K9WPQCCE3R9ZYQ4F1YKT0KP7","organizer_email":"baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.91,"bullets":["Highlighted strong confidence and visibility during recent industry conference, with potential sales momentum.","Baylee assigned Guille as technical marketer to support ABM while retaining account lead role.","Website migration to WordPress is underway; QA and client feedback managed via Bug Herd tool.","Content refresh plans include new landing page work and two approved topics for next month’s articles.","Team aligned on prioritizing case study-led messaging and targeting owners directly for ABM outreach."],"highlights":[{"quote":"I felt the most confident this year at that convention and the most connected.","speaker":"Nick S (GSS)"},{"quote":"We need to make sure that we''re connecting with the owner.","speaker":"Will Fleming"},{"quote":"We will get started talking about some of the ABM stuff...would love your thoughts.","speaker":"Baylee Gunnell"}],"topics":["ABM","content","delivery","website","messaging"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-11-19T12:01:23Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Conference and Networking Impact**\n\nThe team gained valuable industry connections and confidence at the recent conference, setting the stage for future business opportunities. \n\n- **Nick S (GSS)** reported feeling the most confident and connected at this year''s convention, engaging in numerous meetings with prospects, partners, and payroll companies, which led to **a contract already sent out** (00:14).  \n    - This increased networking aligned with strategic goals to build stronger industry relationships.  \n    - The positive sentiment suggests upcoming sales opportunities, though direct sales impact remains uncertain.  \n    - Confidence and familiarity with the marketplace were key factors in this progress.  \n    - This networking momentum supports longer-term pipeline development and partner collaborations.\n\n## **Website Development and Quality Control**\n\nThe website migration is underway with a focus on seamless transfer and quality assurance to support scalable content growth.\n\n- **Baylee Gunnell** and **Will Fleming** confirmed that several pages are built on a staging site, with a **quality control phase** targeting button functionality and visual consistency before final review by the client (03:14).  \n    - A tool called **Bug Herd** will enable real-time client feedback for any adjustments before launch.  \n    - The new platform removes previous page limits, allowing for more flexible content expansion.  \n    - This phased approach reduces risk of errors and enhances user experience upon launch.  \n    - The transition is expected to improve site management and support marketing efforts.\n\n## **Content Strategy and Messaging Refinement**\n\nContent updates are focused on refreshing underperforming pages and developing messaging that resonates with business owners without alienating CFOs.\n\n- The team is refreshing a landing page showing a recent **downtick in engagement** and plans to update WordPress content post-launch (05:20).  \n    - Proposed content ideas include a **30-day CFO assessment** and a **case study highlighting EBITDA improvement**, with emphasis on owner-focused messaging (10:22).  \n    - **Will Fleming** advised avoiding messaging that directly challenges CFO roles, suggesting the focus be on how services provide **financial clarity and relieve burden** rather than replacing CFOs (08:30, 21:49).  \n    - The case study was favored as a trust-building tool showing tangible results and market relevance (18:13, 29:12).  \n    - The messaging aims to help owners envision growth and success without needing deep CFO knowledge.\n\n## **ABM Campaign Targeting and Personalization**\n\nThe account-based marketing (ABM) strategy will target owners and CEOs with tailored messaging designed to build trust and encourage engagement.\n\n- A **new contact list** focusing on owners and CEOs was created to align outreach with decision-makers, with campaign content emphasizing value over free offers to drive 15-minute calls with Nick (14:35).  \n    - Messaging will delicately address issues like financial clarity and accountability without directly questioning existing CFO or controller roles (15:28, 16:36).  \n    - Splitting campaigns based on whether companies have CFOs was considered but deemed potentially inefficient; instead, a unified approach focusing on owners'' perspectives was preferred (24:38, 25:44).  \n    - **Will Fleming** stressed that all messages must go to owners/CEOs, as they are the ultimate decision-makers (26:07).  \n    - Personalization will leverage industry news, company activity, and labor market data to identify high-value targets (27:17).\n\n## **Strategic Positioning and Market Insight**\n\nThe team is aligning messaging and product positioning to address current market challenges and owner priorities amid shifting industry dynamics.\n\n- **Will Fleming** highlighted the importance of showing credibility and trust quickly, especially given downturns in growth and volume pressures in the restaurant sector (29:20).  \n    - Case studies are positioned to demonstrate how the service alleviates owners’ burdens, allowing them to focus on growth without financial worry (20:04, 30:05).  \n    - Messaging will avoid criticizing owners’ gut instincts while promoting data-driven decisions and financial clarity as a growth foundation (29:43).  \n    - The deal with a California group underscores the value of trust and credibility in closing agreements (30:20).  \n    - This approach intends to differentiate the service by focusing on results and relief rather than technical CFO tasks.\n\n## **Operational and Collaboration Enhancements**\n\nThe team is improving collaboration and content development processes to accelerate delivery and maintain quality.\n\n- **Baylee Gunnell** introduced **Guillermo**, a technical marketer brought in to support ABM efforts and backend operations, enhancing capacity without changing account leadership (01:31).  \n    - Plans include interviewing **Will Fleming** to capture expert insights for upcoming articles, ensuring authentic and impactful content (12:39).  \n    - Messaging drafts will be updated collaboratively and shared for review before launch to maintain alignment (31:03).  \n    - The use of tools like Bug Herd streamlines client feedback and reduces turnaround times for site adjustments (03:14).  \n    - These process improvements aim to increase responsiveness and content relevance while supporting scalable marketing efforts.","outline":null,"keywords":["conference networking","website redevelopment","content strategy","CFO services","ABM campaign","owner engagement"],"overview":"- **Conference Success:** Team gained industry connections, leading to a contract sent out and potential sales opportunities.  \n- **Website Migration:** Pages are built on a staging site, focused on quality control and enhanced user experience.  \n- **Content Strategy:** Updating underperforming pages to resonate with owners while ensuring CFOs are not alienated.  \n- **ABM Campaign:** Targeting owners/CEOs with personalized messaging to drive engagement and trust, avoiding CFO challenges.  \n- **Market Positioning:** Emphasizing financial clarity for owners while showcasing service benefits through credible case studies.  \n- **Operational Enhancements:** Improving collaboration and processes for faster delivery and client-centric content development.","action_items":"\n**Baylee Gunnell**\nSchedule an interview with Will Fleming to develop article content on the 30-day CFO assessment and other topics (12:39)\nSend link for Bug Herd tool invite and instructions to Will Fleming and Nick for website feedback (03:14)\nProceed with website build completion and conduct initial quality control (03:14)\nUpdate and refresh landing pages and content per Paula’s optimizations once the new WordPress site goes live (05:20)\nRefine ABM email campaign messaging targeting owners and CEOs, removing overt references to mistrust in CFOs, based on meeting input (15:44)\nDevelop and send updated email messaging concepts for review by Will Fleming and Nick S (31:03)\n\n**Will Fleming**\nProvide input and feedback on content topics, especially the 30-day CFO assessment article (12:39)\nCollaborate on drafting content for articles and ABM messaging (12:39)\n\n**Nick S (GSS)**\nSubmit headshot and podcast materials for marketing use (02:34)\nReview and provide feedback on ABM list and messaging drafts targeting owners/CEOs (14:50)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"0c34ce51-21b9-44a3-b82a-0df29c20ddff","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
