hen this is the only thing that I haven''t figured out.","index":171,"end_time":653.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":650.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I tagged our product marketer to kind of take the lead there, because I''m not sure how she''s going to want to display this.","index":172,"end_time":659.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":653.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":173,"end_time":661.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":660.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Kylie, I don''t know if you were.","index":174,"end_time":662.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":661.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know if you were in that meeting, but we talked about, like, where the integration would go, because I know mostly, like, NCAMP is.","index":175,"end_time":669.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":662.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is pretty much like an isolated solution, right?","index":176,"end_time":673.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":670.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, it doesn''t.","index":177,"end_time":673.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":673.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Doesn''t have to integrate per se, but they.","index":178,"end_time":676.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":673.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They wanted to try to fit that in somewhere.","index":179,"end_time":678.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":676.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This might just get taken out.","index":180,"end_time":680.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":678.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":181,"end_time":681,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":680.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That was kind of up in the air.","index":182,"end_time":682.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":681,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":183,"end_time":683.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":682.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":184,"end_time":683.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":683.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So again, I.","index":185,"end_time":685.6,"